{"tid":595670,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今時今日仍然唔俾着校服入機鋪都幾反智","createTime":"2018-03-17T01:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T12:58:51.000Z","uid":62063,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"087ad5dcbda4562b572e31607388ab89e7e79b67","tid":595670,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>風氣方面</strong><br />\n而家啲機鋪已經唔似當年立例個陣咁係龍蛇混雜之地<br />\n有啲仲要係完全冇煙味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>玩樂方面</strong><br />\n呢條法例基本上係阻止唔到啲學生放咗學唔返歸走去玩<br />\n波樓 K房 戲院 網吧呢啲點解又可以着校服去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>金錢方面</strong><br />\n假設佢唔想學生亂洗錢，點解上面所講嗰啲更高消費嘅活動又唔禁埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當年好鍾意打機，日日放學經過都冇得入去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw而家係咪冇咗跟機文化？"},{"pid":"9b9c3a0052a21cd509cac01751033b73d7a7c062","tid":595670,"uid":38518,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"不嬲on9<br />\n著校服同著便服咪又係同一個人"},{"pid":"2b35afe60b52c896664acc5259c9675e0d062d38","tid":595670,"uid":26937,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"大把人除剩件白背心入去啦"},{"pid":"2ef99679ff5ef0bd025f3422af925b14036deefb","tid":595670,"uid":5375,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:59:15.000Z","msg":"面門問題，夠稱無人阻你，但著校服黎講我係絕對反對，成何體統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，正如去叫雞/佔卜都唔會著高識別度既衫"},{"pid":"ce489d5ad70f7f6ccd355168f9a52ab554b0e0dd","tid":595670,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b35afe60b52c896664acc5259c9675e0d062d38","tid":595670,"uid":26937,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"大把人除剩件白背心入去啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"貼紙遮校章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal